data.description: ELEGANT and METICULOUSLY-MAINTAINED executive home in the Woods at Riverside Village. Gleaming hardwood floors and intricate millwork welcome you into this STUNNING property, featuring a gourmet kitchen, spacious main-level master suite and wonderful, open layout. Main floor has 10' ceilings with windows everywhere that provide gorgeous views to the east-facing backyard, complete with mature landscaping, active stream, vaulted covered patio and lake frontage with water fountain. Perfect for entertaining!
data.whatILove: Master bedroom suite features a fireplace, large sitting area, spacious master bathroom, patio access and a door to the front den/office area, complete with built-in cabinetry. Generously-sized bedrooms upstairs and a bonus room with skylights and newer engineered hardwood floors. Other features include newer 50-yr Presidential shingle roof, new water heater, new refrigerator, new humidifier and some new carpet and interior paint. Master bedroom, master bath and kitchen have been updated in recent years.
